# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
# =============================================================================
# Process Name: MkDocs Nav Generator
# =============================================================================
# Description:
#   Reads mkdocs.template.yml, generates the full nav section from
#   docs/ru/ directory structure and static nav definitions,
#   then writes the complete mkdocs.yml.
#
#   Nav structure:
#     - Static sections (user, admin, dev) defined in NAV_STATIC below
#     - Code Reference section auto-generated by scanning docs/ru/dev/code/
#
# Usage:
#   python scripts/Create-Doc/Generate-Nav.py
#
# File: scripts/Create-Doc/Generate-Nav.py
# Project: AI Assistant (ai_assist)
# Version: 0.8.0
